.DT
set_home_location
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_home_location

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_home_location -  This method will set up a 'home' location for the NPC.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_home_location(string loc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^loc%^RESET%^ - the filename of the room to set as home

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will set up a 'home' location for the NPC.
This is the file name of the room the NPC
should return to whenever it is moved.
It can be used to make unique NPCs returns
to their default location etc.
.EP

